The Firm;;64;;75;;R;;A young lawyer joins a small but prestigious law firm only to find out that most of their clients are on the wrong side of the law. The company is helping to launder mob money, get clients off charges and even murder partners who threaten to blow their cover, but when the FBI come calling to gather evidence on the lawyer's colleagues, he is caught between a rock and a hard place, juggling his life and his liberty.;;Drama,Mystery & thriller;;Sydney Pollack;;1993;;Tom Cruise,Jeanne Tripplehorn,Gene Hackman,Holly Hunter,Ed Harris,Hal Holbrook,Terry Kinney,Wilford Brimley,David Strathairn,Gary Busey,Steven Hill,Tobin Bell,Barbara Garrick,Jerry Hardin,Paul Calderone,Jerry Weintraub,Karina Lombard,John Beal,Sullivan Walker;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1044522-firm